| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1943 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: feaac9c6-9309-519e-98a6-38fe8ea9f6ef"
